\mathbb{P}[\{X \leq x\} \cap \{Y \leq y\}] = \mathbb{P}[\{X \leq x\}] \cdot \mathbb{P}[\{Y \leq y\}].
\mathbb{P}[\{X > x\} \cap \{Y > y\}] = \mathbb{P}[\{X > x\}] \cdot \mathbb{P}[\{Y > y\}]?
