 P(X_1\in A_1, X_2\in A_2, \dots, X_n\in A_n)=\prod_{i=1}^nP(X_i\in A_i) 
P(A \cap B) = P(A) P(B)
 P(A^c \cap B) = P(B - A \cap B) = P(B)-P(A \cap B)=\left(1-P(A)\right)P(B) = P(A^c) P(B).
